(179, NULL, 30, 2, 12, '2', 0, 'variable_product', '2', 'Pure and natural Urad Dal rich in protein, fiber, and minerals', '<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\">Nutritious Urad Dal packed with protein, fiber, and essential minerals for daily meals.</p>', 'pure-and-natural-urad-dal-rich-in-protein-fiber-and-minerals', 1, 0, 0, '', '', 1, 1, 999, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 'uploads/media/2025/ud1.jpg', '[\"uploads\\/media\\/2025\\/ud2.jpg\",\"uploads\\/media\\/2025\\/ud3.jpg\",\"uploads\\/media\\/2025\\/ud4.jpg\",\"uploads\\/media\\/2025\\/ud5.jpg\"]', '', '', 'Urad Dal,Black Gram Dal,Healthy Dal,Protein Rich Pulses,Natural Dal,Indian Pulses,Fiber Rich Dal,Traditional Dal,Nutritious Pulses,Wholesome Dal', '', '', 'India', '0713', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, '<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\">Urad Dal, also known as Black Gram Dal, is one of the most important pulses used in Indian kitchens for centuries. Valued for its high protein, iron, and dietary fiber content, it is considered a wholesome food that supports strength, digestion, and overall well-being.</p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\">This dal is a staple in many traditional Indian recipes, from dal makhani, idli, dosa, and vada to a variety of everyday curries. Its creamy texture and rich flavor make it a versatile ingredient that not only enhances taste but also adds valuable nutrition to your diet.</p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\">Urad Dal is naturally packed with protein, making it an excellent choice for vegetarians who need a reliable source of protein for muscle growth and energy. It is also a good source of iron and calcium, which are vital for bone health and immunity. Its dietary fiber helps improve digestion, regulate cholesterol, and support a healthy heart.</p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\">Regular inclusion of Urad Dal in meals is especially beneficial for growing children, fitness enthusiasts, and elderly people as it provides long-lasting energy and promotes overall vitality. Easy to cook and highly nutritious, Urad Dal is a trusted pulse that continues to hold a special place in Indian households.</p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\">By adding Urad Dal to your daily diet, you are not only choosing taste but also a time-tested food that promotes a healthy lifestyle.</p>', '<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\">Urad Dal is a nutrient-rich pulse that brings both taste and health to your everyday meals. It is naturally rich in protein, fiber, iron, and calcium, making it one of the most beneficial pulses for overall wellness.</p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\">Its versatility is unmatched&mdash;used in north Indian curries like dal makhani or in south Indian dishes like idli, dosa, and vada, Urad Dal fits seamlessly into diverse cuisines. The creamy texture it provides makes dishes more filling and satisfying while keeping them healthy.</p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\">For people seeking a balanced diet, Urad Dal is an excellent option. Its high protein content supports muscle development and energy, while its fiber aids digestion and keeps you fuller for longer. It is also beneficial for heart health and helps maintain healthy cholesterol levels.</p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\">Including Urad Dal in your meals means choosing a wholesome and nourishing food that has been valued for generations.</p>', 1, NULL, 0, '', ' ', 1, 1, NULL, 99, 'Urad Dal – Natural Protein Rich Pulse for Healthy Everyday Meals', 'Urad Dal,Black Gram Dal,Healthy Dal,Protein Rich Pulses,Fiber Rich Dal,Nutritious Pulses,Indian Pulses,Wholesome Dal,Natural Dal,Traditional Pulses', 'Discover the natural goodness of Urad Dal, a protein and fiber-rich pulse that supports digestion, strengthens immunity, and enhances daily meals with taste and nutrition.', '', '2025-09-24 09:18:44');
