cial occasions.</p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\">Apart from sweets, Dudh Malia rice can also be used in certain savory recipes where a soft, creamy grain is desired. It is rich in carbohydrates, providing energy, and also offers small amounts of essential nutrients that make it wholesome as well as delicious.</p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\">Whether preparing a festive kheer or a simple rice pudding, Dudh Malia rice elevates the dish with its smooth texture and authentic flavor. Its ability to turn an everyday dessert into something special makes it a staple for traditional kitchens.</p>', '<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\">Dudh Malia rice is prized for its soft, creamy grains and natural sweetness. Known as the perfect rice for desserts, it is commonly used to make kheer, payasam, and other festive sweets that require a delicate, smooth texture.</p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\">When cooked with milk, sugar, and spices, Dudh Malia rice transforms into a rich, flavorful dish that carries a comforting aroma. This rice absorbs flavors beautifully, making it a favorite among families during celebrations and festive occasions.</p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\">Its tender grains not only provide great taste but also a melt-in-mouth experience. From traditional Indian kitchens to modern dessert recipes, Dudh Malia rice continues to be the go-to choice for sweet preparations that need softness and richness.</p>', 1, NULL, 0, '', ' ', 1, 1, NULL, 12, 'Dudh Malia Rice – Soft Creamy Grains Perfect for Kheer and Desserts', 'dudh malia rice,creamy rice,kheer rice,dessert rice,sweet rice,rice for pudding,malia rice,soft grain rice,Indian dessert rice,rice for payasam', 'Dudh Malia rice is a soft, creamy rice variety ideal for kheer, payasam, and desserts. With tender grains and rich flavor, it’s perfect for festive sweets', '', '2025-09-13 11:12:58'),
