(242, NULL, 30, 6, 23, '2', 0, 'simple_product', '0', 'Sendha Salt – Pure Natural Rock Salt for Health & Wellness', '<p data-start=\\\"298\\\" data-end=\\\"488\\\">Sendha Salt (Rock Salt) is a natural, unrefined salt rich in essential minerals. It&rsquo;s a healthier alternative to regular table salt &mdash; perfect for fasting, Ayurvedic diets, and daily cooking.</p>', 'sendha-salt-pure-natural-rock-salt-for-health-wellness', 1, 1, 0, '', '', 1, 1, 999, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 'uploads/media/2025/Sindhav_Salt_(1).jpg', '[\"uploads\\/media\\/2025\\/Sindhav_Salt_(2).jpg\",\"uploads\\/media\\/2025\\/Sindhav_Salt_(3).jpg\",\"uploads\\/media\\/2025\\/Sindhav_Salt_(4).jpg\",\"uploads\\/media\\/2025\\/Sindhav_Salt_(5).jpg\"]', '', '', 'Sendha Salt,Rock Salt,Sindhav Salt,Himalayan Salt,Natural Salt,Fasting Salt,Ayurvedic Salt,Organic Salt,Mineral Salt,Healthy Salt,Tredify,Pink Salt,Unrefined Salt,Detox Salt', '', '', 'India', '2501', 'DANGI-MILLETS-SALT-001', 100, 1, 0, 0, '<p data-start=\\\"777\\\" data-end=\\\"1142\\\">Sendha Salt, commonly known as Rock Salt or Sindhav Salt, is a natural and unrefined salt formed from ancient mineral deposits. Unlike regular table salt, Sendha Salt is chemical-free and loaded with over 80 essential minerals such as calcium, magnesium, potassium, and iron. These minerals support muscle function, hydration, digestion, and overall body balance.</p>\\r\\n<p data-start=\\\"1144\\\" data-end=\\\"1401\\\">Used widely in Indian households, especially during fasting and detox routines, Sendha Salt is gentle on the stomach and helps maintain the body&rsquo;s natural electrolyte levels. In Ayurveda, it is valued for its cooling, cleansing, and therapeutic qualities.</p>\\r\\n<p data-start=\\\"1403\\\" data-end=\\\"1670\\\">&nbsp;we bring you <strong data-start=\\\"1432\\\" data-end=\\\"1469\\\">100% pure and natural Sendha Salt</strong>, hygienically packed to preserve its freshness and mineral goodness. Perfect for cooking, seasoning, or fasting meals, Sendha Salt adds a natural touch of purity and health to your everyday lifestyle.</p>', '<p data-start=\\\"1724\\\" data-end=\\\"2113\\\"><strong data-start=\\\"1724\\\" data-end=\\\"1739\\\">Sendha Salt</strong> (also called <strong data-start=\\\"1753\\\" data-end=\\\"1769\\\">Sindhav Salt</strong> or <strong data-start=\\\"1773\\\" data-end=\\\"1786\\\">Rock Salt</strong>) is one of the most natural forms of salt available, untouched by pollution and industrial refining. It is mined from mineral-rich rock layers that have existed for millions of years beneath the earth&rsquo;s surface. This pure salt retains its natural structure and contains vital trace elements that promote health and wellness.</p>\\r\\n<p data-start=\\\"2115\\\" data-end=\\\"2494\\\">Known for its pinkish hue and mild taste, Sendha Salt is highly valued in Ayurveda for balancing Vata and Pitta doshas. It aids digestion, enhances nutrient absorption, and helps regulate hydration and pH levels. Because it&rsquo;s free from artificial additives or anti-caking agents, it&rsquo;s an excellent choice for people with high blood pressure or those on detox and fasting diets.</p>\\r\\n<p data-start=\\\"2496\\\" data-end=\\\"2728\\\">Culinarily, Sendha Salt brings out the natural flavors of food without the harshness of refined salts. It can be used in everyday cooking, fasting recipes, pickling, and even as a therapeutic bath salt to soothe the body and mind.</p>\\r\\n<p data-start=\\\"2730\\\" data-end=\\\"2932\\\"><strong data-start=\\\"2730\\\" data-end=\\\"2755\\\">&nbsp;Sendha Salt</strong> is carefully sourced, cleaned, and packed to ensure the highest quality. Embrace the purity of nature &mdash; switch to Sendha Salt for a healthier, more natural lifestyle every day.</p>', 1, NULL, 0, '', ' ', 1, 1, NULL, 50, 'Sendha Salt | Pure Natural Rock Salt (Sindhav Namak) | Ayurvedic & Fasting Salt', 'Sendha Salt,Rock Salt,Sindhav Salt,Natural Salt,Organic Rock Salt,Himalayan Salt,Fasting Salt,Ayurvedic Sa