(243, NULL, 30, 6, 23, '2', 0, 'simple_product', '0', 'Moongaphalee – Natural Protein-Packed Peanuts', '<p>Crunchy, fresh, and full of energy &mdash; <strong data-start=\\\"349\\\" data-end=\\\"374\\\">Moongphalee (Peanuts)</strong> are a powerhouse of protein, fiber, and essential nutrients. Perfect for healthy snacking, cooking, and everyday nutrition.</p>', 'moongaphalee-natural-protein-packed-peanuts', 1, 1, 0, '', '', 1, 1, 999, 1, 0, 0, '', 0, 'uploads/media/2025/Moongphalee_(1).jpg', '[\"uploads\\/media\\/2025\\/Moongphalee_(2).jpg\",\"uploads\\/media\\/2025\\/Moongphalee_(3).jpg\",\"uploads\\/media\\/2025\\/Moongphalee_(4).jpg\",\"uploads\\/media\\/2025\\/Moongphalee_(5).jpg\"]', '', '', 'Moongphalee,Peanuts,Groundnuts,Organic Peanuts,Natural Moongphalee,Healthy Snacks,Protein Snacks,Roasted Peanuts,Tredify,Desi Moongphalee,Indian Groundnuts,Organic Snacks,Nutritious Food', '', '', 'India', '', 'DAN-MOONGPHALEE-001', 100, 1, 0, 0, '<p data-start=\\\"774\\\" data-end=\\\"1211\\\"><strong data-start=\\\"774\\\" data-end=\\\"789\\\">Moongphalee</strong>, also known as <strong data-start=\\\"805\\\" data-end=\\\"830\\\">Peanuts or Groundnuts</strong>, is one of the most nutritious and versatile foods in the Indian diet. Packed with protein, healthy fats, fiber, and essential vitamins, it provides long-lasting energy and supports heart health. Moongphalee is naturally rich in antioxidants like resveratrol and nutrients such as magnesium, iron, and vitamin E, which help in muscle recovery, skin glow, and overall well-being.</p>\\r\\n<p data-start=\\\"1213\\\" data-end=\\\"1464\\\">Perfect as a crunchy snack or as an ingredient in various dishes, peanuts are a favorite across India for their taste and health benefits. Whether roasted, boiled, or added to chutneys and sweets, Moongphalee adds flavor and nutrition to every meal.</p>\\r\\n<p data-start=\\\"1466\\\" data-end=\\\"1719\\\">At &nbsp;we offer <strong data-start=\\\"1491\\\" data-end=\\\"1519\\\">100% natur