rotein Snacks,Roasted Peanuts,Tredify,Indian Peanuts,Organic Food,High Protein Nuts', 'Buy Moongphalee (Peanuts) – 100% natural, protein-rich, and full of healthy fats. Perfect for snacking and cooking. Freshly packed by  for pure taste and nutrition.', '', '2025-10-08 06:15:11'),
