llet  Rice : Replace your regular rice 1:1 with Foxtail or Brown Top millet. Use a 1:2.5 millet-to-water ratio and cook for 15-20 minutes.\n\n    For Gluten-Free Rotis: Grind the Jowar into a fine flour to make soft, pliable bhakris or rotis?a staple for a healthy, gluten-free lifestyle.\n\n    For a Power-Packed Breakfast: Cook Foxtail millet with milk or plant-based milk, add nuts and fruits for a porridge that fuels your morning without weighing you down.\n\nCertifications & Details:\n\n    Certified Organic | 100% Natural | Non-GMO\n\n    Combo Contains: 500g Jowar (Sorghum) + 500g Foxtail Millet + 500g Brown Top Millet\n\n    Naturally Gluten-Free & Vegan\n\n    Rich in Protein, Fiber, Iron, and Magnesium', 1, NULL, 0, '', ' Trepend Shree Dhaan Private Ltd\n2nd Floor, Above Harmony Clinic, Plot D-30, Sarjan Row House, Beside Shreepad Residency, Nr Palanpore Canal Walkway Linear Garden Road, Surat, Gujarat 395009', 1, 1, NULL, 0, 'MilHut Organic Millets Combo (Jowar, Foxtail, Brown Top) | Gluten-Free Digestion & Energy Boost', 'organic millet combo pack, gluten free grains for digestion, jowar sorghum buy online, foxtail millet for energy, brown top millet for weight loss, high protein gluten free diet, ancient grains india, healthy millet cooking, best millets for gut health, buy organic millets online', 'Struggling with low energy & digestion? MilHut\'s Organic Millets Combo Pack with Jowar, Foxtail & Brown Top is your solution. This gluten-free, high-protein grain trio fuels sustained energy, supports gut health & makes healthy cooking easy. Shop the ancient wisdom for modern wellness.\n', '', '2025-11-06 12:57:04'),
