(161, NULL, 30, 2, 12, '', 0, 'variable_product', '2', 'Buy Premium Amarnath Millets Online – Rajgira Superfood for Health, Nutrition & Wellness', '<p>Amarnath Millets (Rajgira) &ndash; a gluten-free, protein-rich ancient grain packed with calcium, iron, and fiber, perfect for fasting, healthy diets, and traditional recipes.</p>', 'buy-premium-amarnath-millets-online-rajgira-superfood-for-health-nutrition-wellness', NULL, 0, 0, '', '', 1, 1, 100, 0, 0, 0, '', 0, 'uploads/media/2025/Amarnath_Millets_(1)1.jpg', '[\"uploads\\/media\\/2025\\/Amarnath_Millets_(2)1.jpg\",\"uploads\\/media\\/2025\\/Amarnath_Millets_(3)1.jpg\",\"uploads\\/media\\/2025\\/Amarnath_Millets_(4)1.jpg\",\"uploads\\/media\\/2025\\/Amarnath_Millets_(5)1.jpg\"]', '', '', 'Amarnath Millets,Rajgira Seeds,Rajgira Flour,Ramdana,Amaranth Grain,Gluten Free Millet,Ancient Superfood,Healthy Millets,Organic Amarnath,Amarnath Benefits', '', '', 'India', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, '<p data-start=\\\"775\\\" data-end=\\\"1103\\\">Amarnath Millets, also known as <strong data-start=\\\"807\\\" data-end=\\\"846\\\">Rajgira, Ramdana, or Amaranth grain</strong>, are one of the most powerful and nutritious ancient superfoods. Packed with protein, fiber, calcium, iron, and essential amino acids, Amarnath is a gluten-free millet that supports overall wellness and is highly recommended for people of all age groups.</p>\\r\\n<p data-start=\\\"1105\\\" data-end=\\\"1506\\\">Traditionally consumed during fasting (vrat/upvas) in India, Amarnath Millets have earned their place as a staple for healthy and energy-boosting recipes. They are widely used in preparing ladoos, chapatis, porridge, khichdi, pancakes, and even baked goods. The nutty flavor and versatility of Amarnath make it easy to include in daily diets while promoting better digestion and long-lasting energy.</p>\\r\\n<p data-start=\\\"1508\\\" data-end=\\\"1844\\\">Nutritionally, Amarnath Millets are known to contain more protein than many other grains, along with lysine &ndash; an essential amino acid not commonly found in other cereals. They are also a rich source of micronutrients like magnesium, phosphorus, and antioxidants, which contribute to heart health, improved immunity, and bone strength.</p>\\r\\n<p data-start=\\\"1846\\\" data-end=\\\"2127\\\">For people with gluten intolerance, diabetes, or those following weight management diets, Amarnath Millets provide a natural, wholesome, and nutrient-dense alternative. Being light yet filling, they help regulate blood sugar levels, support muscle growth, and promote gut health.</p>\\r\\n<p data-start=\\\"2129\\\" data-end=\\\"2387\\\">Choosing Amarnath Millets ensures you are investing in a sustainable, traditional, and health-forward lifestyle. Whether you prefer them as flour, whole grain, or puffed (Rajgira popcorn), this millet is a complete package of taste, culture, and nutrition.</p>\\r\\n<p data-start=\\\"2389\\\" data-end=\\\"2514\\\">Make Amarnath Millets a part of your everyday meals to experience the benefits of an ancient grain trusted for generations.</p>', '<p data-start=\\\"2565\\\" data-end=\\\"2969\\\">Amarnath Millets, popularly called Rajgira in India, have been cherished for centuries as a wholesome food with exceptional nutritional value. Unlike refined grains, Amarnath is naturally gluten-free and suitable for those with dietary restrictions. It is rich in plant-based protein, dietary fiber, and minerals like calcium, iron, and magnesium, making it a perfect superfood for modern health needs.</p>\\r\\n<p data-start=\\\"2971\\\" data-end=\\\"3284\\\">One of the unique features of Amarnath Millet is its use during fasting festivals, where it provides sustained energy and satiety. Beyond traditional recipes, it can also be added to smoothies, granola bars, and modern healthy snacks. Its versatility makes it ideal for both Indian kitchens and global cuisines.</p>\\r\\n<p data-start=\\\"3286\\\" data-end=\\\"3545\\\">Amarnath is also considered an excellent grain for children, athletes, and elderly individuals due to its easy digestibility and nutrient density. By including Amarnath Millets in your diet, you embrace a healthier, balanced, and more sustainable lifestyle.</p>', 1, NULL, 0, '', ' ', 1, 1, NULL, 50, 'Amarnath Millets (Rajgira) – Buy Organic, Gluten-Free, High-Protein Superfood', 'Amarnath Millets,Buy Rajgira Online,Amarnath Flour,Ramdana Seeds,Gluten Free Millets,Rajgira Benefits,Organic Amarnath Grain,Healthy Millets India,Ancient Superfoods,Protein Rich Millet', 'Discover the benefits of Amarnath Millets (Rajgira) – a gluten-free, protein-rich superfood packed with calcium, iron, and fiber. Perfect for fasting, daily nutrition, and healthy recipes. Order pure Amarnath Millet online today.', '', '2025-09-20 09:15:26'),
(162, NULL, 30, 2, 12, '', 0, 'variable_product', '2', 'Buy Browntop Millets Online – Rare, Fiber-Rich, Low GI Ancient Superfood for Healthy Living', '<p>Browntop Millet &ndash; a rare, gluten-free, high-fiber millet with low glycemic index, ideal for diabetics, weight management, and sustainable healthy diets.</p>', 'buy-browntop-millets-online-rare-fiber-rich-low-gi-ancient-superfood-for-healthy-living', 1, 0, 0, '', '', 1, 1, 100, 0, 0, 0, '', 0, 'uploads/media/2025/Brown_Top_Mollets_(1)1.jpg', '[\"uploads\\/media\\/2025\\/Brown_Top_Mollets_(2).jpg\",\"uploads\\/media\\/2025\\/Brown_Top_Mollets_(3).jpg\",\"uploads\\/media\\/2025\\/Brown_Top_Mollets_(4).jpg\",\"uploads\\/media\\/2025\\/Brown_Top_Mollets_(5).jpg\"]', '', '', 'Browntop Millet,Brown Top Grain,Korale,Andu Korralu,Healthy Millets,Rare Ancient Grain,Gluten-Free Millets,Diabetic Friendly Millet,Organic Browntop Millet,High Fiber Grain', '', '', 'India', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, '<p data-start=\\\"763\\\" data-end=\\\"1131\\\">Browntop Millet, also known as <strong data-start=\\\"794\\\" data-end=\\\"828\\\">Andu Korralu, Korale, or Korra</strong>, is one of the rarest and most nutrient-dense ancient grains, cultivated in select regions of India. Recognized for its <strong data-start=\\\"949\\\" data-end=\\\"1029\\\">exceptionally high fiber content, low glycemic index, and gluten-free nature</strong>, Browntop Millet has gained popularity among health-conscious individuals and wellness enthusiasts.</p>\\r\\n<p data-start=\\\"1133\\\" data-end=\\\"1598\\\">Nutritionally, Browntop Millet is rich in dietary fiber, protein, iron, magnesium, calcium, and essential amino acids, making it one of the best millets for balanced nutrition. Its <strong data-start=\\\"1314\\\" data-end=\\\"1336\\\">low glycemic index</strong> helps regulate blood sugar levels, making it an excellent grain for diabetics. The high fiber content supports digestion, promotes satiety, and aids in weight management, while its mineral pr