(8, 'about_us', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>About Us</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Welcome to Homebethe – Your Trusted Natural Marketplace</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">At HOMEBETHE , we\'re on a mission to make healthy living <strong>accessible</strong>, <strong>sustainable</strong>, and <strong>community driven</strong>. We believe that everyone deserves access to pure, chemical free, and ethically produced goods and that’s why we’ve built a platform that connects conscious consumers with passionate natural producers.</p>\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><hr align=\"center\" size=\"2\" width=\"100%\"></div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>What We Do</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Homebethe is more than just an E-Commerce store. It is a <strong>dynamic marketplace</strong> where individuals and families can shop a wide range of <strong>natural products</strong>  from wholesome millets and pulses to eco friendly home essentials  all in one place.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">We also empower <strong>independent vendors</strong> and <strong>tribal women producers</strong> from regions like <strong>Dang district</strong>, giving them a digital platform to showcase their natural, handmade goods made using <strong>traditional wisdom</strong> and <strong>sustainable product</strong>.</p>\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><hr align=\"center\" size=\"2\" width=\"100%\"></div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Why Choose Homebethe?</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>100% Natural Commitment</strong><br>We collaborate only with Seller who follow authentic natural practices  free from chemicals, GMOs, and artificial ingredients.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Empowering Dang Tribal Women</strong><br>Our products are handcrafted by tribal women from Dang, Gujarat  members of self-help groups who gain livelihood, dignity, and financial independence through their work.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Support Local & Small Producers</strong><br>Every purchase supports family run farms, rural entrepreneurs, and women artisans  building a more inclusive economy.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Built for a Better Tomorrow</strong><br>We bridge the gap between nature conscious consumers and honest, sustainable producers  promoting a healthier lifestyle and environment.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Transparency & Trust</strong><br>With complete Seller profiles, sourcing info, and detailed product descriptions  you always know what you’re buying and who you’re supporting.</p>\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><hr align=\"center\" size=\"2\" width=\"100%\"></div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Our Mission & Core Values</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Homebethe places the highest value on <strong>natural principles</strong>, <strong>health focused methods</strong>, and <strong>community empowerment</strong>. In a world dominated by processed and chemical laden foods, our mission is to <strong>revive nature\'s goodness</strong> through genuine, nourishing alternatives.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">We work closely with <strong>Dang’s tribal women</strong>, who hand make every product with care. These women are not just workers  they are our strength and inspiration. give their efforts, we ensure that each item reflects <strong>purity, tradition, and sustainability</strong>.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Health Focused Living</strong><br>Our products are rich in natural nutrition  packed with vitamins, minerals, and fibres to support immunity and Wellness.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Environmental Consciousness</strong><br>We promote natural farming, soil health, water conservation, and biodiversity  because protecting the planet is non negotiable.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">✅ <strong>Strict Quality Control</strong><br>Every item is thoroughly checked for purity and freshness. We never compromise on quality  because your health deserves only the best.</p>\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><hr align=\"center\" size=\"2\" width=\"100%\"></div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p>'),
